divs: Sighting DetailsWell i was at my work in Kennebunk Maine and i was by myself and it was around 2 am in the morning. I went outside to throw away a bag of trash and as i put the bag of trash in the in the bin in the corner of my eye there was a bright light and i turned around there was this hovering object with a blinding light over the trees and without a sound. This encounter lasted around 4 to 7 seconds after on the object just beamed out of nowhere and was gone, this object literally time warped back to wherever it wanted to be.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Kennebunk
There were no other sightings in Kennebunk on or around October 30th 2010
Summary: Bright Light, no sound, hovering, didnt move, close to ground, right above trees,
